05:16.712 --> 05:17.233
That's hope.

05:18.515 --> 05:23.666
So when we talk about hope and healing, hope is bringing light.

05:24.354 --> 05:28.399
Hope is putting light into people's hearts and minds.

05:28.699 --> 05:32.283
That there is a Jesus, there is a God who loves them.

05:32.303 --> 05:39.411
